				<div>Originally Posted by <strong>Tzakapotek</strong></div>
				<div style="font-style:italic">Oh no, the peons are playing at OUR game again. Someone get a stick!<br />
<br />
Big Business is a mercenary business. Anyone who tells you differently is protecting their interest OVER yours, or trying to sell you something.</div>
			
		</td>
